Monday April 24 As the Zungus rebuild and heal, the Ngwenyas retreat to Soweto to lick their wounds. Meanwhile, father and son prepare for the final act of confession and forgiveness. Tuesday April 25 Mehlemamba tells Mpiyakhe that it will not be easy to repay his debt. Beauty prepares to tell her wounded husband the bad news. Wednesday April 26 Zakhiti and Nonhlazi s plight haunts Mpiyakhe and he is determined to help. Mehlemamba suggests a clever plan. Thursday April 27 Judas and Beauty prepare for a dreaded revelation. Qaphela suspects that his cousin is up to no good. Friday April 28 Zama worries about an upcoming appointment with her doctor, while Judas and Beauty are met with a dreadful shock. Judas vows revenge.